      <title>特朗普的乌克兰贸易计划激动的石油稳定到结束周结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-february-14</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一周结束时，石油几乎没有变化，因为交易员正在消化特朗普总统对美国贸易伙伴征收互惠关税的计划，并就结束乌克兰战争的谈判进行谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-february-14</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 23:31:32 GMT</pubDate>
